@[simp]
theorem det_coe_symm {R : Type _} [Field R] {M : Type _} [TopologicalSpace M] [AddCommGroup M] [Module R M]
    (A : «expr ≃L[ ] » M R M) : (A.symm : «expr →L[ ] » M R M).det = (A : «expr →L[ ] » M R M).det⁻¹ :=
  LinearEquiv.det_coe_symm A.to_linear_equiv
#align det_coe_symm det_coe_symm
